                        <item xml:id="a1">
                           <locus/><div style="text-align: justify; line-height: normal;"><span style="font-size: small;">Fol. 8vbc: Donation note extended by the genealogy of ba&#7717;r n&#228;ga&#347;i T&#228;w&#228;ld&#228; M&#228;d&#7723;&#601;n.</span></div><q xml:lang="gez"><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 8vbc: </span></span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt;">&#4829;&#4632;&#4925;&#4624;&#4941;&#4961; &#4824;&#4707;&#4613;&#4653;&#4961; &#4752;&#4875;&#4642;&#4961; &#4720;&#4808;&#4621;&#4848;&#4961; &#4632;&#4853;&#4741;&#4757;&#4961; &#4824;&#4808;&#4608;&#4710;&#4961; &#4616;&#4677;&#4849;&#4661;&#4961; &#4674;&#4653;&#4678;&#4661;&#4961; &#4822;&#4651;&#4961; &#4776;&#4632;&#4961; &#4845;&#4789;&#4758;&#4633;&#4961; &#4632;&#4853;&#4739;&#4754;&#4720;&#4961; &#4645;&#4875;&#4961; &#4808;&#4752;&#4941;&#4661;&#4961; &#4704;&#4632;&#4757;&#4877;&#4645;&#4720;&#4961; &#4656;&#4635;&#4843;&#4725;&#4962; &#4962; &#4962; &#4829;&#4725;&#4813;&#4621;&#4853;&#4961; &#4704;&#4616;&#4811;&#4845;&#4961; &#4739;&#4848;&#4651;&#4961; &#4634;&#4779;&#4772;&#4621;&#4961;&#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4739;&#4848;&#4651;&#4961; &#4634;&#4779;&#4772;&#4621;&#4961; &#4768;&#4709;&#4653;&#4611;&#4637;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4768;&#4709;&#4653;&#4611;&#4637;&#4961; &#4651;&#4873;&#4772;&#4621;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4651;&#4873;&#4772;&#4621;&#4961; &#4824;&#4618;&#4707;&#4758;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4824;&#4618;&#4707;&#4758;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4621;&#4854;&#4961; &#4874;&#4846;&#4653;&#4874;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4808;&#4621;&#4848;&#4961; &#4874;&#4846;&#4653;&#4874;&#4661;&#4961; &#4768;&#4757;&#4851;&#4725;&#4961; &#4873;&#4769;&#4619;&#4845;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4873;&#4769;&#4619;&#4845;&#4961; &#4768;&#4851;&#4757;&#4843;&#4661;&#4961; &#4773;&#4661;&#4677;&#4843;&#4661;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4768;&#4851;&#4757;&#4843;&#4661;&#4961; &#4704;&#4613;&#4653;&#4961; &#4752;&#4875;&#4642;&#4961; &#4720;&#4808;&#4621;&#4848; &#4880;&#4845;&#4723;&#4755;&#4961; &#4878;&#4665;&#4961; &#4773;&#4636;&#4724;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4757;&#4873;&#4645;&#4961; &#4971;&#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4808;&#4773;&#4638;&#4633;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4768;&#4677;&#4616;&#4661;&#4843;&#4961; &#4848;&#4674;&#4673;&#4961; &#4616;&#4707;&#4613;&#4653;&#4961; &#4752;&#4875;&#4642;&#4961; &#4824;&#4813;&#4848;&#4961; &#4720;&#4656;&#4635;&#4961; &#4776;&#4704;&#4848;&#4813;&#4961; &#4709;&#4650;&#4721;&#4961; &#4616;&#4637;&#4616;&#4637;&#4961; &#4768;&#4704;&#4651;&#4669;&#4961; &#4813;&#4708;&#4961; &#4975;&#4808;&#4616;&#4848;&#4961; &#4824;&#4768;&#4901;</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt;">{</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt;">&#4648;</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt;">}</span><span style="line-height: 115%; font-size: 14pt;">&#4846;&#4961; &#4808;&#4824;&#4768;&#4659;&#4768;&#4622;&#4961; &#4704;&#4757;&#4811;&#4846;&#4961; &#4707;&#4613;&#4653;&#4961; &#4752;&#4875;&#4642;&#4961; &#4720;&#4808;&#4621;&#4848;&#4961; &#4632;&#4853;&#4741;&#4757;&#4961; &#4808;&#4709;&#4773;&#4658;&#4721;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4632;&#4853;&#4741;&#4757;&#4961; &#4808;&#4661;&#4632;&#4961; &#4813;&#4617;&#4854;&#4633;&#4961; &#4808;&#4621;&#4848;&#4961; &#4635;&#4653;&#4843;&#4637;&#4961; &#4872;&#4709;&#4648;&#4961; &#4632;&#4661;&#4672;&#4621;&#4961; &#4720;&#4781;&#4616;&#4961; &#4611;&#4845;&#4635;&#4758;&#4725;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4778;&#4851;&#4757;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4846;&#4624;&#4757;&#4661;&#4961; &#4768;&#4632;&#4720;&#4961; &#4645;&#4619;&#4660;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4635;&#4653;&#4843;&#4637;&#4961; &#4808;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4635;&#4653;&#4843;&#4637;&#4961;&#160;&#4808;&#4616;&#4720;&#4961; &#4629;&#4845;&#4808;&#4725;</span></p></q>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note enumerates children of Täwäldä Mädḫǝn. From the beginning till the word ፯ወለደ, it is written in black ink in the same hand as the legends of the miniatures. An identical genealogy of baḥr nägaśi Täwäldä Mädḫǝn, written in the same hand, appears in Ms. UM-029. 
The remaining part of the note is written in a different hand which explains why it is missing from UM-029 (in that Ms. only one of his daughters is mentioned, fol. 84vb l. 31).</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a2">
                           <locus/><p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 139r:<span style="line-height: 115%;"> Record concerning a dispute over the lands between &#705;Ura and </span><span style="line-height: 115%;">&#704;</span><span style="line-height: 115%;">Ag&#228;rh&#601;se. </span></span></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note, written in Tǝgrǝñña, states the result of the court case, the two parties involved, the witnesses and the decision-makers.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="a3">
                           <locus/><p><span style="font-size: small;"><span style="line-height: 115%;">Fol. 180rb:&#160;Ownership note. </span></span></p><q xml:lang="gez"/>
                           <q xml:lang="en"/>
                           <p>The note has been partly erased. It mentions the wife of the donor and other members of his family. It ends with a condemnation formula.</p>
                        </item>
                        <item xml:id="e1">- Tituli of the chapters are written in the upper margins: e.g., fols. 18r, 23v, 29v, 38r, 53r.&#xD;
- Name of a qes gäbäz crudely written in pencil: fols. 180v, 181r. &#xD;
- Ṭälsäm (talisman) picture crudely drawn in pencil: fol. 181r.&#xD;
- Crude minor notes in pen and pencil: fol. 1rv, 9r, 91r.&#xD;
&#xD;
- The miniatures are painted by the same illuminator as in UM-029. Also, the legends are written in the same hand as that of UM-029.</item>
                     </list>
